Device configuration is often the most difficult part of deploying
802.1X and strengthening network access security.
Aruba's ClearPass QuickConnect is a cloud-hosted provisioning utility
and changes this by dramatically streamlining and simplifying device
configuration for IT and end users alike.
ClearPass QuickConnect makes it easy for users to configure 802.1X
authentication on their Windows, Mac OS X, iOS, Android and Linux
devices for more secure network access.
